---
const projects = [
  {
    title: "AI DEV",
    description: "An AI-powered site and chatbot for UCF's AI Club that centralizes events, memberships, and instant Q&A, plugged into Discord for campus-wide engagement.",
    tags: ["html/css"],
    tagStyle: ["gold"],
    links: { learnMore: "#", github: "#" }
  },
  {
    title: "FPL Optimizer",
    description: "An app for Fantasy Premier League where you set constraints and it auto-picks the highest-expected-points squad across future Gameweeks.",
    tags: ["html/css", "python", "socket"],
    tagStyle: ["gold", "gold", "gold"],
    links: { learnMore: "#", github: "#" }
  },
  {
    title: "Location Finder",
    description: "A smart campus finder for amenities, hrestrooms, outlets, printers, and late-night food ranked by distance and crowding.",
    tags: ["AI/ML", "JavaScript"],
    tagStyle: ["gold", "gold"],
    links: { learnMore: "#", github: "#" }
  },
  {
    title: "Project Alpha",
    description: "An advanced machine learning pipeline for real-time data analysis and pattern recognition across UCF's research datasets.",
    tags: ["python", "pytorch"],
    tagStyle: ["gold", "gold"],
    links: { learnMore: "#", github: "#" }
  }
];
---

<section id="projects">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">PROJECTS</h2>
    <p class="projects-desc">
      At the beginning of every semester, members present their work or propose new project ideas.
      If enough people are interested in a project, it is adopted by the club and tech-leads are assigned to lead it.
    </p>
    <p class="projects-desc" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
      All projects are hosted on GitHub under permissive, open source licenses.
    </p>

    <div class="projects-grid">
      {projects.map((p) => (
        <div class="project-card card card-gold-border">
          <h3 class="project-title">{p.title}</h3>
          <p class="project-desc">{p.description}</p>
          <div class="project-tags">
            {p.tags.map((tag) => (
              <span class="tag">{tag}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
          <div class="project-actions">
            <a href={p.links.learnMore} class="btn btn-outline">LEARN MORE</a>
            <a href={p.links.github} target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline">
              GitHub
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h6"/>
                <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/>
                <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #projects {
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  .projects-desc {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .projects-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .project-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .project-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(240, 180, 41, 0.12);
  }

  .project-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .project-desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .project-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .project-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
